---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Now" description="What Michael Linder is doing now — inspired by nownownow.com.">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Now</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-muted">
      Last updated: May 2026 · Inspired by <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-brand-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nownownow.com</a>
    </p>

    <div class="prose mt-10">
      <h2>Professional</h2>
      <p>
        Still working as a Senior Solutions Architect in the platform engineering space for an international semiconductor manufacturer. Current focus: migrating existing CI/CD pipelines to a GitOps-based platform with ArgoCD.
      </p>

      <h2>AI Governance</h2>
      <p>
        Deepening my work on the practical implementation of the EU AI Act for SMEs in the DACH region. Reading a lot, writing some of it down, talking to companies that want to understand what's coming.
      </p>

      <h2>Side Projects</h2>
      <p>
        This website. Building a personal knowledge base around AI Governance that should be useful to others in the long run.
      </p>

      <h2>Personal</h2>
      <p>
        Amateur radio (OE8YML), holiday house in Carinthia, oeradio.at.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
